            "stanza_text": "Je t’apprendrai, chère petite,\nCe qu’il te fallait savoir peu\nJusqu’à ce présent où palpite\nTon beau corps dans mes bras de dieu :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Ta chair si délicate est blanche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Telle la neige et tel le lys ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Ton sein aux veines de pervenche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Se dresse en deux arcs accomplis ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ta chair si délicate est blanche,\nTelle la neige et tel le lys ;\nTon sein aux veines de pervenche\nSe dresse en deux arcs accomplis ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Quant à ta bouche, rose unique,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Elle appelle mon baiser fier ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Mais sous le pli de la tunique,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Rit un baiser encor plus cher.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quant à ta bouche, rose unique,\nElle appelle mon baiser fier ;\nMais sous le pli de la tunique,\nRit un baiser encor plus cher."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Tu passeras d’humble écolière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "J’en suis sûr et je t’en réponds,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Bien vite au rang de bachelière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Dans l’art d’aimer les instants bons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tu passeras d’humble écolière,\nJ’en suis sûr et je t’en réponds,\nBien vite au rang de bachelière\nDans l’art d’aimer les instants bons."
